{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 271032, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 52398, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同求", "timestamp": 1597935533, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 271033, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 52398, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "蹲", "timestamp": 1597935547, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 271042, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 52398, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "先去校医院相关的门诊开转诊，开完记得去校医院的收费的服务台盖章，然后挂北医三院的号去看病，看完记得打印黄色的报销凭证，回来去校医院住院楼的三楼公费报销即可，可以带银行卡，方便直接刷，注意星期四下午不可报销！", "timestamp": 1597935858, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 271102, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 52398, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果是口腔科，一般医生会建议先挂上号再去开转诊单。因为挂号一般会很久，避免超过转诊单时效。口腔科开转诊单不需要很早去排队就可以。", "timestamp": 1597937031, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 271119, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 52398, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: right", "timestamp": 1597937400, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 271127, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 52398, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: C君专业！", "timestamp": 1597937624, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 271134, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 52398, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢", "timestamp": 1597937868, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 271381, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 52398, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 没返校的呢？谢谢", "timestamp": 1597943216, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 271530, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 52398, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 是说异地报销么？没有经历，不过如果是住院的话，一般也是只需要诊断证明和黄色的报销单", "timestamp": 1597969075, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 394467, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 52398, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果是去北医三挂急诊的话记得是不需要转诊单的。有一次过敏比较严重，但校医院皮肤科没号，去挂了北医三急诊，回来顺利报销了。但一定记得要去分诊台盖急诊章。比如黄色的发票和诊断证明一类的票据。报销流程跟c君说的门诊是一样的。", "timestamp": 1601223918, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 37, "pid": 52398, "reply": 10, "tag": null, "text": "求问校外看病报销的流程", "timestamp": 1597935269, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782609, "url": "", "vote": {}}}